
## ffmpeg
# convert to alac
ffmpeg -i input -acodec alac out.m4a
or
-c:a alac
-c:a flac

ref: https://linuxconfig.org/ffmpeg-audio-format-conversions

## profile: high main baseline
ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -c:v libx264 -profile:v main -level:v 4.0 -r 25 output.mp4

